---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Fund Investigator"
  description="Our mission is to make institutional-grade mutual fund analysis accessible to every Indian investor."
>
  <header class="bg-navy pt-32 pb-20 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        Why We Built <span class="text-gold">Fund Investigator</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Moving beyond simple star ratings to understand the <i>true</i> drivers of mutual fund performance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <Section background="white" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-navy font-bold">The Information Gap</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        For years, retail investors in India have been sold mutual funds based on a single metric: <strong>Past Returns</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        But returns tell only half the story. They don't tell you:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-4 my-8">
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>How much risk the manager took to get those returns.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>How the fund behaves during market crashes (Drawdowns).</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>If the "Growth" fund you bought has silently drifted into "Value".</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Institutional investors have access to expensive terminals and analysts to answer these questions. <strong>Fund Investigator exists to give those same insights to you, for free.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" spacing="lg" maxWidth="xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Our Core Principles</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-gold mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Facts, Not Opinions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We don't tell you what to buy. We provide the mathematical evidence—Sharpe ratios, Beta, Alpha—so you can decide.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Zero Conflict of Interest</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We are not a broker. We don't earn commissions. Our only incentive is accurate data.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Scientific Rigor</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our data comes directly from AMFI and public disclosures. Calculations follow standard financial models.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="white" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full bg-gray-200 flex-shrink-0 border-4 border-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
         <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-navy text-white text-3xl font-bold">IM</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-2">Ishpreet Singh Modi</h2>
        <p class="text-gold font-medium mb-4">Founder & Lead Developer</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "I built Fund Investigator because I was frustrated with the lack of depth in retail investment tools. I wanted to see rolling returns and drawdown capture, not just 5-star ratings."
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ishpreetmodi" target="_blank" class="text-navy hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/fundinvestigator" target="_blank" class="text-navy hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
            Follow on X
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Ready to see the data yourself?</h2>
      <Button href="/app" size="lg" icon="arrow-right">Start Analyzing Funds</Button>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>